News
====


Version 0.2.0
-------------

- Many bugfixes
- Ability to update the cluster master candidate list, and the file
  which contains it
- More debugging and more useful log messages
- Ability to support more than one endpoint per cluster
  (but not more than one cluster per endpoint)
- Cache nbma status and updates a node's configuration only on changes
- Route the cluster master ip address over the nbma
- The code is now pylint clean
- Build/Dev system more integrated with ganeti, with the use of a
  submodule (see doc/devnotes.rst)


Version 0.1.0 (initial release)
-------------------------------

- Contains the ganeti nbma initialization scripts (gre, routing, and
  iptables setup)
- Contains the ganeti nld (network lookup daemon) daemon, which updates
  the system with the correct nbma status, from ganeti

